-if success
  %h4 Request sent!
-else
  -if message == "duplicate"
    %h6 Request failed.  Make sure not to send requests to the same opponent on the same stage before they've responded.
  -elsif message == "level"
    %h6 You can't challenge people on the practice stage!
  -else
    %h6 Request failed.  Make sure you're sending the request appropriately and try again.
